  <brief_title>Tissue Sparing Therapy of Female Precancerous Genital Lesions With VITOM</brief_title>
  <acronym>VITOM</acronym>
  <official_title>Development of a Tissue Sparing Procedure for the Diagnosis and Therapy of Female Precancerous Genital Lesions Combining Endoscopic and Ultrasound Technics.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
